            topic_zh: "合同法",
            concept: "Privity of Contract / Consideration / Joint Promisees",
            concept_zh: "合同相对性 / 对价 / 共同受诺人",
            case: "Coulls v Bagot’s Executor and Trustee Co. Ltd (1967) 119 CLR 460",
            principle: "While consideration must move from the promisee, if a promise is made to two or more persons jointly (joint promisees), consideration moving from one of them is sufficient to enable all joint promisees to sue on the promise. However, the doctrine of privity still means only parties to the contract can sue.",
            principle_zh: "虽然对价必须来自受诺人，但如果承诺是向两人或多人共同作出的（共同受诺人），则其中一人提供的对价足以使所有共同受诺人能够就该承诺提起诉讼。然而，合同相对性原则仍然意味着只有合同当事人才能提起诉讼。",
            summary: "Mr. Coulls contracted with O'Neil Construction to allow them to quarry stone from his property, in return for royalties to be paid to him and his wife, Mrs. Coulls, as joint tenants. Mr. Coulls signed the agreement, and Mrs. Coulls also signed (though her role as a party was debated). After Mr. Coulls died, his executor (Bagot's) questioned whether O'Neil should pay royalties to Mrs. Coulls. A majority of the High Court held that Mrs. Coulls was not a party to the contract (as expressed) and had not provided consideration herself. However, some judges indicated that if she had been a joint promisee, consideration from Mr. Coulls would have sufficed for her as well. The case highlighted the distinction and relationship between privity and consideration.",
            summary_zh: "库尔斯先生与奥尼尔建筑公司签订合同，允许其在他的土地上采石，作为回报，奥尼尔公司将向他和他妻子库尔斯太太（作为联权共有人）支付特许权使用费。库尔斯先生签署了协议，库尔斯太太也签了名（尽管她作为当事方的角色存在争议）。库尔斯先生去世后，其遗嘱执行人（巴戈特公司）质疑奥尼尔公司是否应向库尔斯太太支付特许权使用费。高等法院多数法官认为，库尔斯太太并非合同（如所表达的）的一方，并且她本人也未提供对价。然而，一些法官指出，如果她是共同受诺人，库尔斯先生提供的对价对她而言也已足够。该案突出了合同相对性与对价之间的区别和联系。",
            scaffold: "Coulls v Bagot’s Executor and Trustee Co. Ltd explores the relationship between the doctrine of privity and the rule that consideration must move from the promisee, particularly in situations involving joint promisees.",
            scaffold_zh: "库尔斯诉巴戈特遗嘱执行人及受托人有限公司案探讨了合同相对性原则与对价须来自受诺人规则之间的关系，特别是在涉及共同受诺人的情况下。",
            statute: "Common Law of Contract",
            statute_zh: "合同普通法",
