            principle: "A person who is not a party to a contract (a third party) cannot sue upon it or enforce its terms, even if the contract was made for their benefit. This is the doctrine of privity of contract. Furthermore, consideration must move from the promisee; a person cannot sue on a promise unless they have provided consideration for it.",
            principle_zh: "非合同当事人（第三方）不能就合同提起诉讼或强制执行其条款，即使合同是为其利益而订立的。这是合同相对性原则。此外，对价必须来自受诺人；除非一个人为承诺提供了对价，否则不能就该承诺提起诉讼。",
