    principle_zh: "如果合同已化为书面形式，并且书面文件似乎是协议的完整记录，则口头证据规则排除会增加、改变或反驳书面合同条款的外部证据（口头或其他书面证据）。",
    summary: "This rule promotes certainty in written contracts. However, there are several exceptions, including: to prove a custom or trade usage; to clarify ambiguity; to show the agreement was partly written and partly oral (Van den Esschert v Chappell); to establish a collateral contract; to prove misrepresentation, duress, or other invalidating factors; or to show the written document was not intended to be the whole agreement.",
    summary_zh: "此规则旨在促进书面合同的确定性。然而，它有几个例外情况，包括：证明习惯或行业惯例；澄清歧义；证明协议是部分书面和部分口头的（Van den Esschert v Chappell案）；确立附属合同；证明虚假陈述、胁迫或其他导致合同无效的因素；或证明书面文件并非旨在成为全部协议。",
