    topic_zh: "消费者保护法",
    concept: "ACL s 61 - Guarantee: Fitness of Services/Materials for Particular Purpose",
    concept_zh: "《澳大利亚消费者法》第61条 - 保证：服务/材料对特定用途的适用性",
    case: "Ruaro v Holcomm Marine Pty Ltd [2002] FCAFC 174",
    principle: "If a consumer makes known, expressly or by implication, any particular purpose for which services are being acquired, there is a guarantee that the services, and any product resulting from the services, will be reasonably fit for that purpose. This also applies to materials supplied in connection with those services.",
